==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Disbursement
<hw>Dis*burse"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>d⟦eacute⟧boursement</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of
disbursing or paying out.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>disbursement</qex> of the public moneys.</q> <rj><qau>U.
S. Statutes.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is disbursed or paid out; <as>as, the
annual <ex>disbursements</ex> exceed the income</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disburser</ent>⟦br⟧
